      <h2>{{"Download Firefox Adblock Plus"|translate("s60")}}</h2>

      <p>
        {{"Firefox is a free and open source browser available for Windows, OS X, Linux, and Android which supports add-ons. Add-ons are extensions to your browser to improve privacy and security and the way you view the web. Since its launch in 2006, Adblock Plus has continuously been the most popular add-on for the Mozilla Firefox web browser."|translate("s61")}}
