        {{"Adblock Plus for Firefox is more than a popup blocker. Are you troubled by banners, overlays and other annoying advertisements? Just install the Firefox ad blocker and experience the web as it should be. Depending on the filter lists you have activated, you can even block YouTube video ads and block Facebook tracking. Filter lists are created by members of the open source community and free to use. If you don't want to rely on filter lists, you can create your own <a href=\"filters\">blocking rules</a> to customize your web experience."|translate("s62")}}
