        {{"Installing the Chrome Adblock Plus add-on to your browser only takes a few seconds. Simply click the \"Install for Chrome\" button above and confirm the installation by clicking the \"Add\" button. Please note: The Chrome browser displays a warning that Adblock Plus can access the data on any website you visit. This is a standard warning for Chrome extensions running on every tab. We promise to never collect any data about you."|translate("s66")}}
