      <p>
        {{"Add Adblock Plus to your Opera browser by clicking on the green button \"Install for Opera\" above. Click \"Install\" to confirm the installation and to add the extension to Opera. There are no additional steps or configurations necessary, you will automatically be protected against all obtrusive online advertising."|translate("s75")}}
