      <p>
        {{"Adblock Plus for Opera works great. Don't believe us? Don't just take our word for it. Here is what the popular download portal Softpedia has to say: \"Adblock Plus for Opera is a very useful add-on that was especially designed to help users get rid of nuisances like pop-up ads, flashing banners and other such things.\""|translate("s76")}}
      </p>
